        <mxCell id="A9" value="A9. Admin vào Dispute&lt;br&gt;Dashboard &amp; xem xét:&lt;br&gt;• Project contract&lt;br&gt;• Milestone details&lt;br&gt;• Chat history&lt;br&gt;• Deliverable versions&lt;br&gt;• Evidence từ 2 bên&lt;br&gt;• Escrow transaction history" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#000000;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=6;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="835" y="340" width="240" height="152" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
