        <mxCell id="B3" value="B3. Tạo final project summary:&lt;br&gt;• Total amount&lt;br&gt;• Released amount&lt;br&gt;• Refunded amount (nếu có)&lt;br&gt;• Completed milestones&lt;br&gt;• Disputed milestones (nếu có)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#000000;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=6;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="560" y="1225" width="250" height="112" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
